com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core
Interface Reference

All Superinterfaces:
DeployModelObject, Requirement
public interface Reference
extends Requirement

A representation of the model object 'Reference'. A Reference declares an interface that is required by the implementation that backs the ApplicationComponent in order to function properly.

The following features are supported:

  • Range
